Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:43.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlandia... hlavné mesto celej tejto krásy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:48.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde vánok šuští korunami stromov...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde víly spievajú hlasom čistým...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:55.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde kvety len kvitnú...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:58.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde zvony zvonia s ľudskými životmi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:02.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a odrážajú vlny minulosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:05.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hrobka pána bude otvorená
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a zaplníme svet veľkolepou deštrukciou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:16.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že si si zvykol na toto miesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:21.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Cítim sa, ako keby som tu bol od narodenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:34.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu si sa narodil. V zdialenej minulosti a teraz ako...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Prečo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:05.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitaj v Atlandii, kde krídla kvitnú...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:13.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:30.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Pod vysvieteným kopcom sme si vyznali počiatok lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:33.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Kvôli tebe a aj sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:35.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:44.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po tisícročiach osamelosti som sa stretla s tvojim uhrančivým pohľadom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:50.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem byť spojená!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:55.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to príjemný pocit vzrušenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:03:01.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to, ako keby sa táto sila zrodila z morskej peny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:07.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Tieto slzy dojatia, to rozhodne nie je žiaden sen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}toto je útek za láskou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Všetko čo máme sú naše srdcia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Naše nádeje sú v nekonečnej čiernej diere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:24.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem aby, sme boli spojení, a to naveky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:41.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(442,373)}"Nevidené krídla"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:43.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Majster Johannes, bojím sa, že je nakazený vietor v našej svätej Atlandii...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:48.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj Tomu, aby sa o to postaral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stratili sme naše jediné dieťa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:59.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediná nádej, ktorá nám ostala pre strom života je, aby sa sám opelil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:06.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a znesie ovocie stvorenia, predtým než uschne a zomrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:12.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten deň je blízko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je bratov rukopis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slon tancoval" "Slon tancoval"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slon tancoval" "Slon tancoval"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slon tancoval slonie tango"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slon sa točí"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dookola a dookola"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:20.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dookola a dookola, dookola a dookola"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:24.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zabudni na to, nesie ťarchu celého sveta na svojom chrbte"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:51.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia, prepáč. Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem to počuť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Videla si veliteľa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie. Niečo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostal som správu od nadriadených.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:13.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ihneď nevrátime Vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,veliteľ Fudo bude zbavený velenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:46.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa nik nebude o ne starať, ruže zvednú a zomrú...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:05.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo nebol Slnečné Krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:09.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve teraz je to jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve teraz to je o Siriusovi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:16.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi ľúto Silvie. Bol to jej starší brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň s tým!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hľadajú ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš povedať, že je to oddych od rušného života.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiež by som si priala pauzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy to bola pre mňa záhada...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:59.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo je táto základňa na mieste kráľovskej rodiny Alisie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:03.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A prečo tu boli členovia kráľovskej rodiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:14.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo skrývali pod náramkami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Za mnou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak je to tak, tak si pripravená na pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:50.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevoniaš veľmi šťastne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:56.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako môžem byť?! Ako môžem byť šťastná?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:09:01.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glena a Siriusa stretlo nešťastie len vďaka mne...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:29.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Siriusa niečo úbohé trápilo a urobil hlúposť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:34.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Videl si tajmostvo, ktoré mal Sirius pod náramkom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, jasné...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:41.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak akože ťa to netrápi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Mal som niečo spraviť?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:58.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda... Ľudia, ktorí sú nešťastní, robia hlúposti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:02.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vybrala som si nešťastie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:09.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Poď so mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:39.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nám dala zvrhlá kráľovská rodina do rúk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:58.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je Shangri-la, jedno z hlavných miest ľudskosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:03.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Shangri-la? Večné mesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:09.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale hovorí sa, že zaberie storočie, aby vyrástla o 1 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Týmto to trvalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:15.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...12.000 rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,12.000 rokov?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:29.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to zakladatelia hlavných miest: Apollonius a Seliane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:38.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve tu ľudstvo našlo spôsob, ako sa postaviť Ťieňovým Anjelom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vynašlo sa tu veľa techniky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vraví sa, že sa narodil človek, ako Ťieňový Anjel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a Ťieňový Anjel ako človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:56.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto lokácia bola dôležitá, pre riadenie Aquariona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:02.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmierna moc je vraj v týchto ruinách.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A preto ste zvrhli Siriusovu kráľovskú rodinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:12.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich náramky zakryli pierka Ťieňových Anjelov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to potomkovia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apolloniusa, ktorý aj keď bol Ťieňový Anjel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,sa zaľúbil do človeka a zničil svet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:33.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a Seliane, ktorá bola človek, sa zaľúbila do Ťieňového Anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to môže byť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dve duše sa stali jednou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:48.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedna sa rozdelila na dve a potom do troch duší: Aquariona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:05.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si ma sem priviedol?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:07.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:11.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale je nádherné. A nevonia pekne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Lahodné...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Starec Fudo my raz povedal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:31.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Na jar, aj keď nie je objavená, tak vždy kvitne."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To my nedáva zmysel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:17.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď, Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:23.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ver vo mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odmietla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:56.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, bolo to hrubé prerušenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám iné možnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prišiel sem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol tu Sirius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechoď!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmieš ísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto povedal, že nás znova nezradí?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to spravil Apollonius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už ma znova nezradí...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože zdedí krídla anjelov.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:44.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale jeho polovica nie je s nami, ale proti nám!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto bude tvoj 1. boj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:56.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš bojovať so svojimi bývalými priateľmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Priateľmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som žiadneho nemal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:25.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš pilotovať... Vector?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcete ma na tejto misii?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentoraz to nepustím z ruky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak choď.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýtická sila prichádza! Mýtická sila prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:00.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zapnite bariéry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vysoko úrovňové kvantové vzorce potvrdené!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to... Vector Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Mars?! Je to Sirius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:18.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Vrátil si sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne je to Sirius?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:27.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak je to Sirius, tak prisahám...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius! Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si to ty, nie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika! Nechoď za ním!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerob to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius! Počúvaj ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:46.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nežiadam o odpustenie! To, čo som urobial, je neospravedlniteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:51.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak neprestanem veriť ľuďom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:57.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius! Prosím ťa! Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veriť? Komu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty bastard! Ako to môžeš robiť priateľovi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:25.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Anjelský Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherubín Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Mars a Cherubín sa dostali do Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:12.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 sekundy. To mi stačí na to, aby som ťa porazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:16.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 sekundy?! Neber ma na ľahkú váhu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:45.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Nič nefunguje!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to beznádejné! Predvída každý náš krok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:56.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozerajte, ako zničím Deavu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:59.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vectory Sol a Luna sú nepoužiteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepriateľ sa približuje veľkou rýchlosťou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Systém bariéry sa preťažuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Máme stav núdze!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:11.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rezonácia vectoru Mars ničí bariéru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Týmto tempom, sa sem dostane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:20.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:23.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno by sme sa mali začať modliť?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 neidentifikované objekty sa blížia veľkou rýchlosťou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nová zbraň?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za vibráciu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže to byť? Vyzerá to ako...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci! Všetko je pod kontrolou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:20.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozeráte sa na Útočného Aquariona,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:22.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,vybudovaného spoločne Deavou a Novými Spojenými Národmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:30.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia a všetci... Pozerajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite, čo ľudia spravili Anjelom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo ste spravili svojim priateľom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:50.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rastie na ňom perie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:56.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen? Si to ty Glen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:46.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudia konečne prekročili neprekročiteľnú čieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:49.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a pochopili zakázanú technológiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:52.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže byť toto nešťastie zastavené?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:55.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Ľahké krídla"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:57.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednoť sa so mnou!\N Zastavte ich niekto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:59.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(459,404)}"Ľahké krídla"
